result.adr_address: 76-78 Woosung St, Jordan, Hong Kong
result.name: Luen Fat Seafood Restaurant

reviews.text: Much better service than other fish restaurants around. Reliable in pricing. I ordered steamed grouper and was tasty.

Would definitely recommend this restaurant, all the dishes were yummy and really good value for money in term of the quality you got. Went back to my hometown Hong Kong for a short holiday and randomly came across this restaurant as it had been recommended by several local media. AND it really did not disappoint! 

My family and I really enjoyed our meal there, especially the seafood dishes. Yet my favourite was one of the cold dish - jellyfish with shredded chicken salad. It got all the flavours right, slightly spicy with a hint of sourness given by the pickled cucumbers and carrots! Yum Yum~ a must try beside all the seafood dishes, and not to mention, the portion was ENORMOUS! 

The atmosphere was casual and service was OK. It's not the best definitely but was expected and acceptable in old districts like Jordan area, at least the waiters had been responsive and polite. As heard from the member of staff, the restaurant has been in business for more than 30 years and just got renovated recently. Thus, it was quite clean and bright. 

I will definitely go again when I am in town and recommend it! Just wish to have discovered this tiny gem earlier.
Very good chinese food

First night in Hongkong. We stepped in quite randomly attracted by the aquariums outside. Turned out to be a very lucky shot as the seafood was really really really good. We had all sorts of shellfish and noodles. Every dish tasted great and on top of that, the service was excellent. Would visit again.
Getting value and friendly service

result.adr_address: 香港佐敦吳松街76-78號
result.name: 聯發海鮮菜館

reviews.text: 전체적으로 음식이 짜다. 가리비 사이즈가 커서 1인당 1개씩 주문해도됨. 음식이 많이 짜서 공깃밥시켜서 먹어야됨. 찻값에 부가세까지 포함되면 가격이 센펀임
2019年4月7日零晨一時光顧，坐低叫完食物後，隔離枱有人點烟，我立即要求轉位，點知去到另外一個廳時，其他客人將成包烟放在枱面，亦有吸完的烟頭，我話要走，不吃了！店員話帶我去二樓，怎知去到都有人在吸烟，但佢自己話吸，之後叫了白粥，在粥内有無數黑色一點點的東西，衛生好有問題！ 🙄🙄
食物價廉美味美但地方一般
Much better service than other fish restaurants around. Reliable in pricing. I ordered steamed grouper and was tasty.

近隣には有名海鮮料理屋も多い並び。周りの店にもかなり通いましたがこの店は適正な価格で、質の良い食事をとりたい際にお薦めです。ホタテ貝は蒜蓉蒸扇貝、マテ貝は鼓椒炒聖子で、それぞれ一つが60HKD前後、白灼中尿蝦も時価で一本118HKD程度(単価ですからね、写真の一皿にはそれぞれ十個載ってます)　写真はありませんがビールを呑むのであれば、牛油白飯魚(65HKD) もぜひ頼んで、カシューナッツ入で大変美味しい。
